 {'from': 'human', 'value': "Well, I've been struggling with addiction for a while now. I thought by now I would have overcome it and be in a better place, but it feels like I'm stuck in this vicious cycle. No matter how hard I try to break free, I keep falling back into old habits. It's consuming me, and I don't know how to escape."}
