 {'from': 'human', 'value': "I've noticed that the more I engage with support groups and therapy, the less alone I feel in my struggles. I have learned the importance of self-care, setting boundaries, and developing healthy relationships. I now have a renewed sense of hope and believe in my ability to overcome my addiction. It's a daily journey, but one I am determined to navigate with courage and resilience."}
