 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Exactly, Charlie! Trusting yourself and embracing your passions are key aspects of finding happiness in any new hobby. Remember, it's not about being the best or meeting unrealistic expectations, but rather about enjoying the journey and allowing yourself the space to grow and learn. As you rediscover your love for playing the guitar, I encourage you to approach it with a mindset focused on self-compassion and nurturing your own creativity."}
