[{'from': 'human', 'value': "Hi Alex! I've been feeling really excited lately, but there's something that's been on my mind - work-related stress. It's been taking a toll on me, and I want to address it, you know? I think it goes back to my childhood, where there were certain expectations that I felt I had to meet in order to be loved and accepted."}
