 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Your willingness to consider seeking help is a brave and significant step, Charlie. It takes strength to acknowledge when we need support in navigating challenging family dynamics. Remember that you are deserving of love, understanding, and a sense of belonging within your family. If you decide to pursue mediation or counseling, I'll be here to provide guidance and support along the way."}
