[{'from': 'human', 'value': "Hi Alex, I hope you're doing well today. I just wanted to reach out because lately, I've been feeling quite lonely. It's been a few months since my divorce was finalized, and while I'm happy with the decision I made, I can't help but feel this lingering sense of emptiness in my life."}
