 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "It's completely understandable to have those fears, Charlie. Opening up to someone can make us feel vulnerable, but it's important to remember that your feelings are valid and deserve to be heard. You deserve a harmonious relationship with your mom, and your concerns and emotions matter. If it feels overwhelming, remember to take breaks during the conversation if needed and breathe."}
 {'from': 'human', 'value': "Thank you, Alex. Your words and guidance really give me the strength to approach this conversation with a new perspective. I'll try my best to stay calm and open-minded, and I'll definitely take breaks if it becomes too much for me. I believe that change is possible, and I'm motivated to work towards a healthier relationship with my mom."}
