[{'from': 'human', 'value': "Hi Alex, I hope you're doing well today. I've been struggling with anxiety lately, and I could really use your support and guidance. You see, I've always been a bit shy and self-doubting, but recently I started dating this incredible woman. She's my girlfriend now, and I want to be confident in our relationship."}
