 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "You're very welcome, Charlie. It's an honor to support you in your healing journey. Remember, healing takes time, and it's normal to feel overwhelmed at different stages. I'm here for you whenever you need someone to listen or offer guidance. You're incredibly brave for opening up and seeking support."}]

