[{'from': 'human', 'value': "I'm really struggling with work-related stress, Alex. It's been weighing me down, and I don't know how to cope with it anymore. I feel tense all the time, and it's affecting my happiness in life. I want to find a way to overcome this and start feeling more at peace. Can you help me?"}
