 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Alongside self-care practices, it may be beneficial to assess and communicate your boundaries at work, Charlie. Establishing clear expectations with your colleagues and superiors can help prevent overwhelm and promote a more manageable workload. It's essential to remember that it's okay to ask for support when needed. Additionally, organizing your tasks and prioritizing them can provide a greater sense of control. How do you feel about exploring boundaries and task management?"}
