 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "I appreciate your willingness to try a new approach, Charlie. Overcoming the fear of disappointing others is a common struggle, and it often stems from high internal standards. Let's explore the underlying beliefs that contribute to this pressure. Are there any specific situations or past experiences that you think might be influencing your desire to constantly prove yourself?"}
