 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "That's a beautiful realization, Charlie. Acknowledging your strengths and accomplishments allows you to honor yourself and your journey. As you continue to focus on your own worthiness, remember that finding peace is a continuous process. It's normal to have ups and downs, but by nurturing self-compassion and practicing self-care, you can navigate work-related stress with greater resilience. Is there any specific action or intention you would like to set moving forward?"}
