 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "You're welcome, Charlie. It takes time and effort, but it is possible to overcome these challenges. One approach we can explore is cognitive-behavioral therapy (CBT), which aims to help you reframe your thoughts and develop healthy coping mechanisms. It's about challenging those negative beliefs and building a more positive self-image. How does that sound to you?"}
