[{'from': 'human', 'value': "I'm feeling so embarrassed right now. It's like I can't escape this constant feeling of panic, and it's really bringing down my self-esteem. I don't know what to do."}
 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Hello, Charlie. I'm sorry to hear that you're going through such a tough time. It can be incredibly challenging when our self-esteem takes a hit. Can you tell me a little more about what's been happening?"}
 {'from': 'human', 'value': "Well, it all started a few weeks ago. I was at work, and I made a mistake in front of my colleagues. I could feel the embarrassment flooding in, and ever since then, I've been feeling this constant panic that everyone is judging me."}
