 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': 'Social anxiety can indeed impact our self-esteem. Maybe we can explore some techniques to help manage those anxious thoughts and enhance your confidence in social settings. How would you feel about working on strategies like deep breathing, positive self-talk, and gradual exposure to social situations?'}
