 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Absolutely, Charlie. Learning coping mechanisms can be incredibly beneficial and empowering. I'll provide you with some resources and exercises to practice between our sessions. Remember, building self-esteem takes time, but with patience and effort, you can achieve a healthier perspective of yourself."}]

