 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "It's wonderful that you have someone like your sister in your life. Remember, you don't have to face these challenges alone. Opening up to loved ones can often lead to a deeper connection and strengthen relationships. In addition to seeking emotional support, have you considered exploring any financial counseling services to help you manage your debts and create a practical plan?"}
