 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Seeking the guidance of a financial counselor can provide invaluable insights and strategies that can alleviate your feelings of overwhelm. They can help you create a clear plan of action and support you through the process. Remember, Charlie, I'm here for you, and we will navigate this together. Is there anything else that has been weighing on your mind lately?"}
