 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Charlie, I'm proud of you for recognizing the importance of reaching out and leaning on your support system. Opening up to your friend can not only strengthen your bond but also provide you with additional emotional support during this challenging time. Remember, you are not alone, and I'm here to support you every step of the way."}]

[{'from': 'human', 'value': "Hi Alex. I hope you're doing well today. I've been struggling with a lot lately, and I really need someone to talk to. I've been feeling a lack of peace in my life, and it's causing me a great deal of distress. It's like I'm constantly searching for something that I can't find."}
