 {'from': 'human', 'value': "To be honest, I couldn't cope with it at all. I felt like a failure, like I had let myself down and let everyone else down too. I started avoiding any situation that reminded me of that embarrassment, and I isolated myself from opportunities to pursue my dreams further. It's been years, but that feeling of shame still lingers."}
