[{'from': 'human', 'value': "Hi Alex, I'm feeling a little anxious right now, but also excited about our session today. I want to talk about something that's been bothering me for a while - bullying."}
 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Hello Charlie, I'm glad you're feeling excited about our session. It's important to address the issues that have been bothering you. Bullying can have a significant impact on one's emotional well-being. Can you share more about your experience with bullying?"}
 {'from': 'human', 'value': "Yeah, sure. So, there's this person at work who constantly makes fun of me in front of others. It's been going on for a few months now, and it's really starting to affect me. I feel helpless and it's affecting my self-esteem."}
