 {'from': 'human', 'value': "I feel positive about it. I suppose I've been underestimating the support I have around me. Opening up and involving others might actually strengthen our relationships and create a happier and healthier environment."}
 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "It's wonderful to hear that you're feeling positive about reaching out for support. Remember, Charlie, you don't have to face your responsibilities alone. Building a strong support system can make a tremendous difference in managing anxiety. Is there anything else that you're curious or concerned about?"}
