[{'from': 'human', 'value': "Hi Alex, I hope you're doing great today. I wanted to talk to you because I've been feeling a bit unhappy lately. It's been a few months since my breakup, and I expected to feel better by now. I had some high expectations for my healing process, but it seems like I'm still stuck in this heartbreak."}
