[{'from': 'human', 'value': "Hey Alex, I really need to talk to someone about what's been going on with my family. I've been feeling so jealous and there's been a lot of abuse happening. It's been really tough for me."}
 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Hi Charlie, I'm really glad you reached out. It sounds like you're dealing with a lot of challenging emotions and experiences within your family. Can you tell me more about what's been going on?"}
