 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Those are fantastic goals, Charlie. Building effective communication skills and finding healthy ways to manage jealousy are both important aspects of fostering positive family dynamics. I'm confident that we can work together to achieve these outcomes. As we move forward, it's crucial to remember that you are in control of your therapeutic journey. I'll be here to support you every step of the way, but the direction we take will be guided by your needs and preferences. Are you ready to embark on this journey of self-discovery and growth?"}
